modName: Davos Jkar Pack Mule Companion Follower
summary: Davos J\'kar Pack Mule Companion Follower in Helgen Keep
descriptionHtml:
Davos J\'kar Pack Mule Companion Follower finds refuge in Helgen Keep during the dragon attck, he is more than eager to carry your extra equiptment, however will let you do all the fighting!
Davos is carrying the ingredients for my other mod \"Fine Leather Armor\" based on the Linwe armor which has had the enchantment removed and is craftable and enchantable!

All credit goes to Bethseda for this mod as It is a manipulation of existing data to provide the set!
author: DanielRColgan
